I have been making the dish regularly since it first appeared in Bon Appetit. Since I have two vegetarians in the house I make a few changes to compensate for not using the sausage: I double the mushrooms, add chopped sun dried tomatoes and a little dried fennel. I also increase the spicing. Everyone loves it and it is healthy as well. Great recipe!

